171
00:10:40,850 --> 00:10:41,650
Dongchao?

172
00:10:43,610 --> 00:10:44,420
Lingling.

173
00:10:45,420 --> 00:10:46,580
This is Mr. Chen Mo.

174
00:10:46,580 --> 00:10:47,850
He's been my main contact here.

175
00:10:49,490 --> 00:10:50,300
Mr. Jiang.

176
00:10:51,370 --> 00:10:52,700
