188
00:11:13,650 --> 00:11:14,340
Next year,

189
00:11:14,340 --> 00:11:16,220
our school's equipment

190
00:11:16,580 --> 00:11:18,010
and even the dormitory beds

191
00:11:18,010 --> 00:11:19,610
