195
00:11:32,420 --> 00:11:33,220
No problem.

196
00:11:39,700 --> 00:11:40,490
Please accept this.

197
00:11:42,820 --> 00:11:43,890
You're too kind, Mr. Bai.

198
00:11:44,820 --> 00:11:46,460
I heard your birthday is coming up,

199
00:11:47,060 --> 00:11:49,010
so consider this a gift.

200
00:11:50,430 --> 00:11:51,490
I appreciate the thought,

201
00:11:51,820 --> 00:11:52,770
