207
00:12:06,100 --> 00:12:06,890
Mr. Bai,

208
00:12:07,770 --> 00:12:08,890
if you have any questions,

209
00:12:09,180 --> 00:12:09,980
just ask.

210
00:12:10,300 --> 00:12:11,700
I'll tell you anything

211
00:12:11,770 --> 00:12:12,700
that I know.

212
00:12:19,340 --> 00:12:20,890
I've been back for a while now,

213
00:12:21,180 --> 00:12:22,250
and all I do is play golf

214
00:12:22,250 --> 00:12:23,650
with Mr. Jiang every single day.

215
00:12:24,490 --> 00:12:26,060
He hasn't said a word about

216
00:12:26,850 --> 00:12:28,180
my position in the company.

217
00:12:29,980 --> 00:12:31,220
I was wondering if you could

218
00:12:33,220 --> 00:12:34,580
give me some inside information?

219
00:12:36,650 --> 00:12:38,490
Actually, Mr. Jiang gave us
his instructions

220
00:12:38,490 --> 00:12:39,770
long before you returned.

221
00:12:41,060 --> 00:12:42,130
He feels that

222
00:12:42,420 --> 00:12:44,100
