226
00:12:56,180 --> 00:12:57,010
If you ask me,

227
00:12:57,850 --> 00:12:58,650
Mr. Bai,

228
00:12:59,490 --> 00:13:00,530
stop worrying about

229
00:13:00,530 --> 00:13:01,340
