230
00:13:01,890 --> 00:13:03,100
and just focus on yourself.

231
00:13:03,180 --> 00:13:04,340
It'll be better that way.

232
00:13:06,460 --> 00:13:07,250
Anyway,

233
00:13:07,460 --> 00:13:08,770
