235
00:13:09,770 --> 00:13:10,820
I've got a lot on my plate.

236
00:13:11,010 --> 00:13:11,580
Goodbye.

237
00:13:13,060 --> 00:13:14,180
What about the gift?

238
00:13:15,370 --> 00:13:16,180
You should

239
00:13:16,250 --> 00:13:17,700
