240
00:13:17,980 --> 00:13:18,980
I'm sure she'll love it.

241
00:13:29,700 --> 00:13:34,660
(Chen Mo: Today is a special day.
Can I take you out for dinner?)

242
00:13:37,860 --> 00:13:41,380
(Rao Yuci: I can't tonight.
I have something important to discuss.)

243
00:13:49,420 --> 00:13:50,770
