245
00:14:05,890 --> 00:14:07,060
(I'm sorry, Chen Mo.)

246
00:14:09,730 --> 00:14:11,460
(I need to face this on my own.)

247
00:14:15,100 --> 00:14:17,730
(I don't want to drag you into this mess.)

248
00:14:35,420 --> 00:14:37,900
