253
00:15:12,660 --> 00:15:14,180
About what you mentioned last time...

254
00:15:14,370 --> 00:15:15,420
I've made up my mind.

255
00:15:17,890 --> 00:15:18,890
Let's work together.

256
00:15:20,670 --> 00:15:22,250
Let's take down Bai Liangliang together.

257
00:15:26,220 --> 00:15:27,650
But you know what she's like.

258
00:15:28,730 --> 00:15:29,770
If we want to beat her,

259
00:15:31,060 --> 00:15:32,650
