00:29:23,420 --> 00:29:24,010
of the project

564
00:29:24,010 --> 00:29:25,530
will win you Mr. Jiang's trust?

565
00:29:25,980 --> 00:29:27,290
You're so naive.

566
00:29:28,140 --> 00:29:30,220
You really think
you're that important, don't you?

567
00:29:30,660 --> 00:29:32,220
I'm just doing my job.

568
00:29:34,140 --> 00:29:35,330
Mr. Jiang, I'll be going now.

569
00:29:46,660 --> 00:29:48,090
(On this path within Lysen Group,)

570
00:29:49,900 --> 00:29:51,570
(there can be no more mistakes.)

571
00:29:53,730 --> 00:29:54,900
(I must hide my true self.)

572
00:29:56,380 --> 00:29:57,810
(I can't let anyone see through me,)

573
00:29:57,810 --> 00:29:59,570
(that I need friendship or love.)

574
00:30:01,420 --> 00:30:02,890
(And if I don't hide it well enough,)

575
00:30:04,330 --> 00:30:06,140
(they will become my weaknesses.)

576
00:30:08,460 --> 00:30:10,050
(Don't repeat the same mistakes.)

577
00:30:11,290 --> 00:30:12,090
(Remember,)

578
00:30:13,620 --> 00:30:15,220
(solitude is my only armor.)

579
00:30:15,220 --> 00:30:21,020
ظآزAnd I'm standing
on the traumatized ruins unbentظآز

580
00:30:21,740 --> 00:30:27,510
ظآزTil the day my kingdom's reclaimedظآز

581
00:30:31,050 --> 00:30:33,420
The Green Building Materials project
is back with Dept 3,

582
00:30:33,980 --> 00:30:35,700
so let's make sure we do it right.

583
00:30:36,660 --> 00:30:37,250
But if we

584
00:30:37,250 --> 00:30:38,810
actually pull this off,

585
00:30:38,810 --> 00:30:40,290
should we start calling you...

586
00:30:42,250 --> 00:30:43,140
"Director Yu".

587
00:30:44,290 --> 00:30:45,090
Stop joking around.

588
00:30:45,730 --> 00:30:46,900
Great results come from focus.

589
00:30:47,140 --> 00:30:48,460
Let's use this opportunity

590
00:30:48,460 --> 00:30:49,900
to get Dept 3 back on its feet.

591
00:30:49,980 --> 00:30:50,570
Manager Yu,

592
00:30:50,570 --> 00:30:51,290
I'm not asking you

593
00:30:51,290 --> 00:30:52,730
to help me take down Bai Liangliang.

594
00:30:53,180 --> 00:30:53,860
But look at

595
00:30:53,860 --> 00:30:55,090
the current state of Dept 3.

596
00:30:55,730 --> 00:30:57,180
If we don't show some ambition,

597
00:30:57,730 --> 00:30:59,420
Lysen Group will soon phase us out.

598
00:31:00,050 --> 00:31:00,860
So,

599
00:31:01,420 --> 00:31:02,330
just like me,

600
00:31:02,910 --> 00:31:04,460
you need to climb up to have a chance.

601
00:31:04,460 --> 00:31:09,840
ظآزWhen the moon comes out I ask myselfظآز

602
00:31:11,200 --> 00:31:17,630
ظآزWill forgiveness
help me sleep at nightظآز

603
00:31:19,240 --> 00:31:22,230
ظآزTwo wrongs don't make a rightظآز

604
00:31:29,290 --> 00:31:30,090
Manager Yu.

605
00:31:31,180 --> 00:31:32,140
Let's get going.

606
00:31:35,380 --> 00:31:36,940
Boss, if you really want to drink,

607
00:31:37,220 --> 00:31:39,090
we'll stay with you
for as long as you need.

608
00:31:39,190 --> 00:31:40,460
But can we do it somewhere else?

609
00:31:41,600 --> 00:31:42,980
- Good evening, Director Ren.
- Good evening, Director Ren.

610
00:31:44,490 --> 00:31:46,180
We'll head out first then.

611
00:31:46,430 --> 00:31:47,380
Goodnight, Director Ren.

612
00:32:10,140 --> 00:32:11,330
Aren't you allergic?

613
00:32:12,180 --> 00:32:13,570
Since when did you start drinking?

614
00:32:15,090 --> 00:32:16,380
I picked it up after the breakup.

615
00:32:46,180 --> 00:32:47,970
Did I make a complete fool
of myself today?

616
00:32:50,420 --> 00:32:52,090
You should have been prepared for this.

617
00:32:54,530 --> 00:32:56,100
You know Mr. Jiang better than anyone.

618
00:32:58,180 --> 00:32:59,330
Everything Rao Yuci is

619
00:32:59,330 --> 00:33:00,180
going through today...

620
00:33:02,050 --> 00:33:03,290
I've been through it all before.

621
00:33:05,530 --> 00:33:06,660
From underdog to big shot.

622
00:33:12,010 --> 00:33:13,220
This is the path I chose.

623
00:33:17,460 --> 00:33:18,620
The path you chose...

624
00:33:20,050 --> 00:33:22,050
So you're seeing it through,
no matter the cost?

625
00:33:26,980 --> 00:33:28,250
Is that why you chose

626
00:33:29,810 --> 00:33:31,700
to throw away ten years of love?

627
00:33:49,330 --> 00:33:50,180
At Lysen Group,

628
00:33:51,880 --> 00:33:53,220
feelings don't count for anything.

629
00:33:53,940 --> 00:33:55,380
If you want to stay at Lysen,

630
00:33:56,490 --> 00:33:57,810
you have to stand alone.

631
00:33:58,180 --> 00:33:59,290
Break up, then?

632
00:33:59,730 --> 00:34:01,180
What kind of excuse is that?

633
00:34:02,330 --> 00:34:03,530
Between the two of us...

634
00:34:07,290 --> 00:34:08,490
Only you wanted

635
00:34:08,490 --> 00:34:09,210
to stay in Lysen.

636
00:34:19,300 --> 00:34:20,940
So the more I want to protect...

637
00:34:24,940 --> 00:34:26,490
the more I have to leave behind.

638
00:35:08,050 --> 00:35:09,790
It's been a while
since we walked together.

639
00:35:14,860 --> 00:35:15,980
Walk with me for a bit.

640
00:35:32,220 --> 00:35:35,700
=Episode 12=
(No Place for Compassion)

641
00:35:36,380 --> 00:35:38,820
(All animals in this production
were treated humanely)

642
00:35:38,820 --> 00:35:45,020
ظآزTake a breath and swallow
the words you couldn't sayظآز

643
00:35:45,780 --> 00:35:48,980
ظآزNo need to force your heart anymoreظآز

644
00:35:48,980 --> 00:35:53,500
ظآزSearching for the season
we once missedظآز

645
00:35:53,500 --> 00:36:01,020
ظآزLeave this place,
though wounded still stay strongظآز

646
00:36:01,020 --> 00:36:04,940
ظآزYou must believe
one day the rain will fallظآز

647
00:36:04,940 --> 00:36:08,980
ظآزAnd wash away the mud
that stains your soulظآز

648
00:36:08,980 --> 00:36:12,500
ظآزFind your freedom in the wildظآز

649
00:36:12,500 --> 00:36:16,460
ظآزTake your stride and move aheadظآز

650
00:36:16,460 --> 00:36:20,620
ظآزI will stay behind
and wait for your eyesظآز

651
00:36:20,620 --> 00:36:24,820
ظآزTo rebuild
the same flesh and soul againظآز

652
00:36:24,820 --> 00:36:28,620
ظآزWander freely through the thornsظآز

653
00:36:28,620 --> 00:36:32,700
ظآزKeep walking through the lightظآز

654
00:36:32,700 --> 00:36:36,900
ظآزFate is absurd, don't stop for anyoneظآز

655
00:36:36,900 --> 00:36:43,220
ظآزWhat you dare to lose
will one day be your ownظآز

656
00:37:00,340 --> 00:37:06,980
ظآزI'm sorry, I still owe you these wordsظآز

657
00:37:06,980 --> 00:37:10,820
ظآزAn apology that came too lateظآز

658
00:37:10,820 --> 00:37:15,460
ظآزYet it's also the path
that saves my soulظآز

659
00:37:15,540 --> 00:37:22,940
ظآزWhen the cold wind
passes it takes the past awayظآز

660
00:37:22,940 --> 00:37:27,020
ظآزYou must believe and stand unwaveringظآز

661
00:37:27,020 --> 00:37:31,100
ظآزThere will be hands
to pull you from the deepظآز

662
00:37:31,100 --> 00:37:35,100
ظآزFind your freedom in the silenceظآز

663
00:37:35,100 --> 00:37:38,860
ظآزLet your wounds be mendedظآز

664
00:37:38,860 --> 00:37:43,060
ظآزGray is not the past
and pain is not a shameظآز

665
00:37:43,060 --> 00:37:47,220
ظآزSometimes the sunlight
makes the world look cruelerظآز

666
00:37:47,220 --> 00:37:50,940
ظآزWander through the echoes of regretظآز

667
00:37:50,940 --> 00:37:54,980
ظآزBe forgiven and be shelteredظآز

668
00:37:54,980 --> 00:37:59,020
ظآزAfter everything shatters,
hold my handظآز

669
00:37:59,020 --> 00:38:05,220
ظآزA flower reborn
will finally bloom foreverظآز
